description: Don't miss this turn-key South Boston one bedroom condo! Conveniently located just one block from West Broadway and all of its shops and restaurants. Easy street level living with assigned parking spot! Step though the door into a tiled foyer with coat closet, then up a few steps into the bright living area. Galley style kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances, Corian counter tops and tile floor. The freshly painted living room and bedroom, with hardwood flooring throughout make this unit totally move-in ready. Exceptional storage with four closets in the unit plus an additional storage locker. There is laundry in the building. Relax outside in the common outdoor seating area. Unit is vacant, easy to show, and ready for its next owner!
